* Multiple\nExpectations
** Python: Stack Decorators
***_ Multiple @dp.expect decorators
***_ Separate rules per column
***_ Different actions per rule
** Python: Dictionary Groups
***_ Define rules as dict
***_ expect_all / expect_all_or_drop
***_ expect_all_or_fail
***_ Reuse across tables
** SQL: Multiple Constraints
***_ Comma-separated CONSTRAINT lines
***_ In CREATE OR REFRESH table
***_ Per-constraint actions
** Benefits
***_ Comprehensive validation
***_ Consistent rule sets
***_ Reduced duplication
***_ Maintainable quality rules
@endmindmap
